 \"a musical director\", \"from\": 3691, \"to\": 3709}, {\"ngram\": \"keyboardist\", \"from\": 3711, \"to\": 3722}, {\"ngram\": \"arranger\", \"from\": 3724, \"to\": 3732}, {\"ngram\": \"programmer\", \"from\": 3737, \"to\": 3747}, {\"ngram\": \"such artists\", \"from\": 3774, \"to\": 3786}, {\"ngram\": \"Onree Gill\", \"from\": 3846, \"to\": 3856}, {\"ngram\": \"Jimmy Jam\", \"from\": 3869, \"to\": 3878}, {\"ngram\": \"Sting\", \"from\": 3896, \"to\": 3901}, {\"ngram\": \"21 Savage\", \"from\": 3956, \"to\": 3965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has also served as musical director of two Off-Broadway musicals, \\\"Mighty Real: A Fabulous Sylvester Musical\\\" and \\\"An Evening with Phyllis Hyman.\\\"\", \"from\": 4076, \"to\": 4225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4210, \"end\": 4223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phyllis_Hyman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.64641637368416e-55, \"text\": \"Phyllis Hyman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phyllis_Hyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phyllis_Hyman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"musical director\", \"from\": 4098, \"to\": 4114}, {\"ngram\": \"two Off-Broadway musicals\", \"from\": 4118, \"to\": 4143}, {\"ngram\": \"Mighty Real\", \"from\": 4146, \"to\": 4157}, {\"ngram\": \"A Fabulous Sylvester Musical\", \"from\": 4159, \"to\": 4187}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"An Evening\", \"from\": 4193, \"to\": 4204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A full circle moment for Harris was having the chance to collaborate with some pioneers in the industry.\", \"from\": 4227, \"to\": 4331, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A full circle moment\", \"from\": 4227, \"to\": 4247}, {\"ngram\": \"Harris\", \"from\": 4252, \"to\": 4258}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 4270, \"to\": 4280}, {\"ngram\": \"some pioneers\", \"from\": 4301, \"to\": 4314}, {\"ngram\": \"the industry\", \"from\": 4318, \"to\": 4330}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Meeting and working with four people (the late Michael Mathis, Rickey Minor, Ray Chew and Onree Gill) who I looked up to, growing up and observing as musicians and musical directors, has been a blessing because it was like working and getting to know my music director heroes.\\\"\", \"from\": 4333, \"to\": 4611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4397, \"end\": 4409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rickey_Minor\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rickey Minor\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rickey_Minor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rickey_Minor\"}, {\"begin\": 4411, \"end\": 4419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Chew\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ray Chew\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Chew\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Chew\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Meeting\", \"from\": 4334, \"to\": 4341}, {\"ngram\": \"four people\", \"from\": 4359, \"to\": 4370}, {\"ngram\": \"the late Michael Mathis\", \"from\": 4372, \"to\": 4395}, {\"ngram\": \"Onree Gill\", \"from\": 4424, \"to\": 4434}, {\"ngram\": \"musicians\", \"from\": 4484, \"to\": 4493}, {\"ngram\": \"musical directors\", \"from\": 4498, \"to\": 4515}, {\"ngram\": \"a blessing\", \"from\": 4526, \"to\": 4536}, {\"ngram\": \"my music director heroes\", \"from\": 4585, \"to\": 4609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The unifying power of music Honors in his career that have meant the most to him are those that bring people together.\", \"from\": 4613, \"to\": 4732, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The unifying power\", \"from\": 4613, \"to\": 4631}, {\"ngram\": \"music Honors\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4647}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 4651, \"to\": 4661}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4715, \"to\": 4721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was part of the Grammy's 2021 Song of the Year \\\"I Can not Breathe,\\\" which represented the fight against police brutality in the inspiration of the George Floyd incident,\\\" Harris said.\", \"from\": 4734, \"to\": 4920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4753, \"end\": 4759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grammy_Awards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7835177192380863e-23, \"text\": \"Grammy\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grammy_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grammy_Awards\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 4741, \"to\": 4745}, {\"ngram\": \"the Year\", \"from\": 4775, \"to\": 4783}, {\"ngram\": \"the fight\", \"from\": 4823, \"to\": 4832}, {\"ngram\": \"police brutality\", \"from\": 4841, \"to\": 4857}, {\"ngram\": \"the inspiration\", \"from\": 4861, \"to\": 4876}, {\"ngram\": \"the George Floyd incident\", \"from\": 4880, \"to\": 4905}, {\"ngram\": \"Harris\", \"from\": 4908, \"to\": 4914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Another proud moment was when I performed a song I co-produced and arranged on the 2023 ESPY awards to honor Jimmy Valvano's speech on its 30-year anniversary to \\\"Never Give Up\\\" in honor of the V Foundation for cancer research.\", \"from\": 4921, \"to\": 5149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5116, \"end\": 5128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jim_Valvano\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"V Foundation\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jim_Valvano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jim_Valvano\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another proud moment\", \"from\": 4922, \"to\": 4942}, {\"ngram\": \"a song\", \"from\": 4964, \"to\": 4970}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2023 ESPY awards\", \"from\": 5001, \"to\": 5021}, {\"ngram\": \"Jimmy Valvano's speech\", \"from\": 5031, \"to\": 5053}, {\"ngram\": \"its 30-year anniversary\", \"from\": 5057, \"to\": 5080}, {\"ngram\": \"honor\", \"from\": 5103, \"to\": 5108}, {\"ngram\": \"cancer research\", \"from\": 5133, \"to\": 5148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Projects that are special to me are those that advance us as humans and bring us together rather than tear us apart.\\\"\", \"from\": 5150, \"to\": 5267, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Projects\", \"from\": 5150, \"to\": 5158}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5205, \"to\": 5207}, {\"ngram\": \"humans\", \"from\": 5211, \"to\": 5217}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5228, \"to\": 5230}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5257, \"to\": 5259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When working on a new project, Harris said he always thinks back to this quote: \\\"We are only as good a musician as our sample bank.\\\"\", \"from\": 5269, \"to\": 5401, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new project\", \"from\": 5285, \"to\": 5298}, {\"ngram\": \"Harris\", \"from\": 5300, \"to\": 5306}, {\"ngram\": \"this quote\", \"from\": 5337, \"to\": 5347}, {\"ngram\": \"only as good a musician\", \"from\": 5357, \"to\": 5380}, {\"ngram\": \"our sample bank\", \"from\": 5384, \"to\": 5399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have to be conscious musicians, but also conscious humans,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 5403, \"to\": 5475, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"conscious musicians\", \"from\": 5418, \"to\": 5437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"By studying great music, we understand the textures that combine to formulate wonderfully made music whether produced, performed, arranged or composed.\", \"from\": 5476, \"to\": 5628, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"great music\", \"from\": 5489, \"to\": 5500}, {\"ngram\": \"the textures\", \"from\": 5516, \"to\": 5528}, {\"ngram\": \"wonderfully made music\", \"from\": 5555, \"to\": 5577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And even beyond actual music, life itself from its various experiences is even more important than the music because it fuels the inspiration for the music that relates to others to reflect and connect us even more.\\\"\", \"from\": 5629, \"to